<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD//XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Test: Column-width applied to 'display: list-item'</title>
        <link rel="author" title="Microsoft" href="http://www.microsoft.com/" />
        <link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-multicol/#cw"/>
        <meta name="flags" content="" />
        <meta name="assert" content="The 'column-width' property applies to elements of 'display: list-item'."/>
        <style type="text/css">
            #parent
            {
                font: 20px/1 monospace;
                margin-left: 2em;
                position: relative;
            }
            #multicolumn
            {
                color: red;
                display: list-item;
                column-width: 5em;
            }
            #multicolumn, #reference
            {
                height: 6em;
                width: 11em;
            }
            #reference
            {
                color: green;
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
            }
            #reference div
            {
                position: absolute;
                width: 5em;
            }
            #right
            {
                right: 0;
            }
            #marker
            {
                display: list-item;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Test passes if there is a marker to the left of the first line of text and there is no red visible on the page.</p>
        <div id="parent">
            <span id="multicolumn">
                AAAAAAAAA BBBBBBBBB CCCCCCCCC DDDDDDDDD EEEEEEEEE FFFFFFFFF GGGGGGGGG HHHHHHHHH IIIIIIIII JJJJJJJJJ KKKKKKKKK LLLLLLLLL
            </span>
            <div id="reference">
                <div id="marker">AAAAAAAAA BBBBBBBBB CCCCCCCCC DDDDDDDDD EEEEEEEEE FFFFFFFFF</div>
                <div id="right">GGGGGGGGG HHHHHHHHH IIIIIIIII JJJJJJJJJ KKKKKKKKK LLLLLLLLL</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>